    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dive into the delightful world of fish farming and fishing in this short experimental idler, <strong>Bit-cremental: Fishistry!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3287300/extras/04c8fbdadb15ac98c2d6bf1d1be527f8.poster.avif?t=1737766263\" width=800 height=449 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3287300/extras/04c8fbdadb15ac98c2d6bf1d1be527f8.webm?t=1737766263\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Grow and feed your stock, earn money as fisher people reel in mature fish, and upgrade to unlock rare species and colorful new designs, all set in a charming Game Boy-inspired style.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3287300/extras/d7fa7feb9d6bb33997b657eecd70a9f7.poster.avif?t=1737766263\" width=800 height=448 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3287300/extras/d7fa7feb9d6bb33997b657eecd70a9f7.webm?t=1737766263\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Gameplay Features:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Fish Growth:</strong> Grow your fish and aquatic creatures from tiny eggs to fully grown wonders.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Fish Discovery System:</strong> Encounter 24 different fish types based on rarity, and strive to discover them all!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Idle and Active Gameplay:</strong> Play actively or let your fishery grow while you’re away with automatic idle progression.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Game Boy Inspired Graphics and Sounds:</strong> Play a piece of nostalgia with a retro inspired pixel art from the 90's handheld era with a crunchy audio track.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Customize:</strong> Add a personal touch to your fishery with unlockable backgrounds and color palettes.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Upgradeable Fishery:</strong> Improve your fishery with upgrades like better feed, fish value, and fish capacity.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Simple &amp; Relaxing Play:</strong> A short, laid-back gameplay experience perfect for casual gaming with incremental progression.</p></li></ul>",
